reviewText: This Zumba dvd is exactly what it says.  It lasts about 20 minutes and it is fast and tough.  If you are in a hurry and need to really workout hard this is a great dvd!  The music is great the instructor is great and the moves are great.  You won't be disappointed.
The commentary takes some getting used to. It will serve the purpose but I will explore other DVDs as well.
